Nyonya Besar.

26
00:01:57,950 --> 00:01:58,400
Ini…

27
00:01:59,830 --> 00:02:01,590
Tak boleh menolak
pemberian senior.

28
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,300
Cepat ambil.
Katakan terima kasih.

29
