(Nenek Keluarga Su, Su Wangshi)

30
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:05,360
Ambillah.

31
00:02:10,270 --> 00:02:11,520
Terima kasih, Nyonya Besar.

32
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:18,360
Masih berani memanggil "Nenek"?

33
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:22,240
Ada pepatah, "Kurangi komentar saat
makan dan terima barang orang".

34
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,320
Kau menumpang tinggal
di rumah kami.

35
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:26,180
Apa yang akan kau kurangi?

36
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:26,880
Kurangi ambisi.

37
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:27,800
Kau…

38
00:02:28,750 --> 00:02:30,540
Su Wei, Xiaoman.

39
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,240
Kalian berdua ikut aku.

40
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:49,110
Sudah bisa berbohong?

41
00:02:50,190 --> 00:02:52,030
Nilai ujianmu kali ini
begitu jelek.

42
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,940
Masih berani bilang yang
tidak-tidak soal Xiaoman.

43
00:02:55,110 --> 00:02:55,800
Berlututlah!

44
00:02:59,030 --> 00:03:00,030
Istriku.

45
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:00,930
Istriku, jangan marah.

46
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:01,670
Aku saja.

47
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,030
Su Minggu!

48
00:03:08,270 --> 00:03:10,390
Kejujuran merupakan
fondasi dasar seseorang!

49
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:15,270
Sekarang, kau sudah terbiasa
semena-mena dan berbohong.

50
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,680
Sekarang berani menutupi
nilai sekolah.

51
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:21,520
Kelak, entah masalah sebesar apa
yang akan kau sebabkan.

52
00:03:26,470 --> 00:03:27,520
Hari ini, tak perlu sarapan.

53
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,360
Berlututlah di sini!

54
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,880
Saat waktunya tiba,
pergi sendiri ke sekolah.

55
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:37,190
Kau ini.

56
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:40,900
Jangan sarapan lagi.
Makan siang yang banyak.

57
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,600
Istriku, tunggu aku.

58
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,240
Istriku.

59
